# Linux Internals Deep Dive

Boot sequence:

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram

Firmware->>GRUB: Start

GRUB->>Kernel: Load

Kernel->>initramfs: Initialize

initramfs->>Filesystem: Mount Root

Filesystem->>systemd: Start Init

systemd->>Services: Launch
```

Every failure occurs somewhere in this chain.

